  	    "headline": "Mitt Romney\u0027s Republican Presidential Campaign - GQ April 2012",
  	    "alternativeHeadline": "Yes, it seems that Mitt Romney has been running for president forever. But we did some digging, and you don\u0027t know the half of it. As Robert Draper discovered, Romney has been driven by a force larger than himself for a very long time",
  	    "url": "http://gq.com/story/mitt-romney-republican-primary-gq-april-2012",
  	    "image": ["http://media.gq.com/photos/5583079809f0bee56440ea3e/master/pass/news-and-politics-2012-04-mitt-romney-romney-628.jpg"],
  	    "thumbnailUrl": "http://media.gq.com/photos/5583079809f0bee56440ea3e/master/pass/news-and-politics-2012-04-mitt-romney-romney-628.jpg",
