Trending Right This Very Second</h3><p class="dek" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.1"></p><section class="component-feature-list" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2"><div class="feature-list-item" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0"><div class="feature-item-index" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.0">1</div><section class="feature-item" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0"><div class="feature-item-image" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.0"><a class="feature-item-link" href="http://gq.com/story/these-pants-will-replace-your-favorite-khakis-in-no-time" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.0.0"><img class="feature-item-thumb" src="http://media.gq.com/photos/56256ceca7113fb922cd872c/1:1/w_100/mr-porter-1115-ami.jpg" alt="" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.0.0.0"></a></div><div class="feature-item-content" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.1"><div class="feature-item-rubric" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.1.$0">Style</div><h3 class="feature-item-hed" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.1.$1"><a class="feature-item-link" href="http://gq.com/story/these-pants-will-replace-your-favorite-khakis-in-no-time" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-0.$0.1.$1.0">These Pants Will Replace Your Favorite Khakis in No Time</a></h3></div></section></div><div class="feature-list-item" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-1"><div class="feature-item-index" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-1.0">2</div><section class="feature-item" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-1.$1"><div class="feature-item-image" data-reactid=".ips856yg3k.1.1.0.1.0.0.0.1.2.1:$ft-item-1.$1.0"><a class="feature-item-link" href="http://gq.com/story/signs-you-should-shave-your-head" data-reactid=".ips856yg